I got more tricks where that came from!


* Iron Raptor growled and watched as her charges went wide a bit but two of 
them striking Scattershot in the back.
She smiled.*

" You should know by now not to turn your back on the enemy, Scattershot. It 
can be bad for your health!"

* She called to him in a light hearted tone, but keeping her guns aimed 
towards him.
But her mind wasn't only on him, sje was also keeping a watchful scanner on 
Nemisis above her.
She didn't trust just leaving a bot like that to make up whatever attack he 
was going to do. But at the moment both him and Scattershot were fairly far 
appart and she couldn't attack both at once.
So while she delt with one it gave the other time to think and act out an 
attack.
Which was none to her banifit.
Iron Raptor snapped her head towards Nemisis Enforcer as he fired at her, 
knowing that she couldn't avoide all the shots he fired at her.
So she did the next best thing: retrecting the guns back into place she 
quickly armed herself with her shield and braced herself, hearing the 
charges hit heavily and nearly knock herself off her feet.
The insignea on the shield glowed as it took in the energy from the blasts.
Soon the sword would be powered again and she might have a chance to finish 
Nemisis.*
